Q1
Compile and run both server and client code.
Enter a file required by client and press enter. Server sends file to client
Enter 'exit!' and server and client both exit.

Q2 (Same for persistent and non persistent)
Run both server and client.
Enter a file required by client and press enter. Server sends file to client
Enter 'exit!' and server and client both exit.

Note: We put our data files in server folder since we only noticed the requirement of data folder at the end moment while submitting.

